      <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
         <ul class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">  The status of the record is either <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Awaiting</uicontrol> or <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Delegated</uicontrol>.</li>
         </ul>
